Description: record short animated GIF images from your screen
 A simple tool that allows you to record short animated GIF images from your screen.
 .
 Currently only Linux with X11 is supported.
 Other Unix like systems using X11 should work as well.
 It is planned to also support Wayland and maybe other operating systems in the future.
